Current Data

Our survey data (including vector images of the plans and extended elevations) are in the following git repository on GitHub:

github.com/jarvist/migovecsurveydata

We also register all of our discoveries with the official Slovenian land register, the kataster jam. For example here is the registration for M16.

Survey Data Archives

For mostly outdated cave registration data, please see The Caves of Migovec.
